Reasoning: The paper introduces a new logic, robust LTL, and studies its verification and synthesis problems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-category. However, the paper also deals with many-valued semantics and the notion of robustness, which are relevant to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). The verification and synthesis problems are also relevant to Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
